#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:172
msgid "Wasted Wind"
msgstr "Wasted Wind"

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:173
msgid ""
"\n"
"    a data project by Robin Hawkes about wasted wind energy in Great "
"Britain. I am grateful for that work as a model for explaining curtailed "
"renewables in a clear, public-facing way.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    un proyecto de datos de Robin Hawkes sobre energía eólica "
"desperdiciada en Gran Bretaña. Le agradezco ese trabajo como modelo para "
"explicar renovables vertidas de forma clara y accesible.\n"
"    "

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:180
msgid "About"
msgstr "Acerca de"

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:182
msgid ""
"\n"
"    I built Wasted Sun as a private individual to put unused solar in "
"plain sight. It is not an official\n"
"    Octopus Energy product, website, or communication.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Creé Wasted Sun como particular para dejar el solar no utilizado a la"
" vista. No es un producto, sitio web\n"
"    ni comunicación oficial de Octopus Energy.\n"
"    "

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:188
msgid ""
"\n"
"    I care strongly about this topic, including through my role as Head "
"of Technology at Octopus Energy\n"
"    Spain—but unless stated otherwise, the analysis and opinions here are"
" mine alone and do not represent\n"
"    my employer.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Me importa mucho este tema, también por mi trabajo como director de "
"Tecnología en Octopus Energy España;\n"
"    salvo que se indique lo contrario, el análisis y las opiniones aquí "
"son solo mías y no representan a mi empleador.\n"
"    "

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:197
msgid ""
"\n"
"  Figures are derived from Red Eléctrica de España data and processed "
"independently for this site;\n"
"  they are not official REE publications or government statistics.\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"  Las cifras proceden de datos de Red Eléctrica de España y se procesan "
"de forma independiente para este sitio;\n"
"  no son publicaciones oficiales de REE ni estadísticas gubernamentales.\n"
"  "

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:203
